    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                <pb facs="nei.j4b.4.1-3"/>
                <note type="curatorial">1</note>
                <note type="curatorial">Piper Collection</note>
                
                <opener>
                    
                    <dateline>
                        Jan. 3rd 23
                    </dateline> 
                    
                    <salute>Dearest Miss Piper!</salute>
                </opener>
                
                <p>You were perfectly sweet to send me those beautiful stockings, and I appreciate them, and the kind thoughts you took of me! Many, many thanks!</p> 
                <p>The children were de-
                lighted write your funny ani-mals! I am keeping mother's package for her, as she is so "on the go" now, and I think she will enjoy her xmas gifts more upon her return to home and quiet.</p> 
                <p>Baby Alice is such a big</p> 
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4b.4.1-3"/>
                <note type="curatorial">2</note>
                
                <p>girl now, and talks so sweetly!</p> 
                <p>I wish she had been as big as she is now last summer, so that I could have gone about more with you!</p> 
                <p>Mother has been having a lovely time, and I am so glad she could go.</p> 
                <p>John leaves for his next trip north on the eleventh.</p> 
                <p>We are all well and as happy as now be-</p>
                <p>I hope you had a lovely time Christmas, and that she new year holds much good for you!</p> 
                <closer>
                    <salute>Ever cordiallly-</salute>
                    <signed>Mona Neihardt</signed>
                </closer> 
                
            </div1>
            
            <div1 type="envelope">
                <pb facs="nei.j4b.4.1-3"/>
                <note type="curatorial">3</note>
                <note type="curatorial">19 Piper Collection</note>
                
                <ab type="postmark">
                    BRANSON JAN. 4 3 AM
                </ab>

                <ab type="address">
                    Miss Mildred Piper. 
                    809 North Hastings Ave
                    Hastings
                    Nebraska 
                </ab> 
                
            </div1>
